OPERATION STEALTH:

                              SOLUTION


    AT VARIOUS POINTS IN THIS GAME CONTROL OF JOHN WILL BE TAKEN OVER BY THE
    COMPUTER IN THESE PLACES ALL I HAVE DONE IS PUT THE NEXT COMMAND AFTER
    THE CONTROL RETURNS TO THE PLAYER (USUALLY IN A DIFFERENT LOCATION).


    EXAMINE COIN RETURN SLOT ON MACHINE TO LEFT
    USE COIN ON COIN SLOT
    ENTER DOOR TO LEFT
    ENTER RIGHT HAND TOILET
    OPERATE BRIEFCASE
    TAKE PEN
    TAKE AMERICAN PASSPORT
    OPERATE CALCULATOR
    TAKE UNUSED PASSPORT
    EXAMINE NEWSPAPER AND SET PASSPORT FALSIFIER TO THE COUNTRY MENTIONED
    USE UNUSED PASSPORT ON OPENING
    OPERATE ENTER BUTTON
    OPERATE BRIEFCASE
    LEAVE TOILETS
    USE FALSE PASSPORT ON CUSTOMS OFFICIAL
    SPEAK TO WELCOME HOSTESS
    EXIT LEFT
    USE AIRLINE TICKET ON GUARD
    EXIT LEFT ABOVE "SALIDA" SIGN
    TAKE BLUE BAGGAGE (MR MARTINEZ)
    OPERATE BAGGAGE
    EXIT RIGHT
    ENTER DOOR ON RIGHT
    OPERATE ELECTRIC RAZOR
    USE ELECTRIC CABLE ON PLUG SOCKET
    LEAVE TOILETS
    USE FALSE PASSPORT ON CUSTOMS OFFICIAL
    EXIT LEFT
    EXIT AIRPORT
    WAIT AT TAXI STAND
    ENTER TAXI
    EXIT LEFT
    ENTER BANK
    USE NOTES ON BANK TELLER
    USE NOTES ON BANK TELLER
    EXIT RIGHT
    EXIT RIGHT
    USE COINS ON FLORIST
    TAKE RED CARNATION
    USE CARNATION ON JOHN
    EXIT LEFT
    EXIT TOP LEFT BEHIND BANK
    CLICK ON PARK BENCH UNTIL JOHN SITS DOWN
    EXIT BOTTOM RIGHT QUICKLY AFTER SHOOTING ETC
    ENTER BANK
    USE KEY AND CARD ON BANK TELLER
    EXIT BOTTOM
    USE KEY ON BOTTOM RIGHT SAFE
    TAKE LITTLE BOX
    TAKE ENVELOPE
    OPERATE GROUND
    USE CORDS ON PIECE OF METAL (METAL BY JOHNS ELBOW)
    OPERATE METAL
    WALK SLIGHTLY UP AND LEFT OF WHERE JOHN WAS SITTING
    OPERATE PICK AXE (DO THIS AT DIFFERENT POSITIONS UNTIL A HOLE STARTS TO
    APPEAR IN THE WALL AND THEN OPERATE PICK AXE 3 TIMES)
    WALK RIGHT,THROUGH THE HOLE IN THE WALL
    ON THE NEXT THREE SCREENS YOU NEED TO SWIM OVER TO THE RIGHT OF THE 
    SCREEN BUT KEET COMING UP FOR AIR AND ALLOW YOUR OXYGEN BAR TO BE FULLY
    REJUVENATED.(PRACTICE MAKES PERFECT ON THESE SCREENS)
    WHEN YOU APPEAR OUT OF THE WATER EXIT LEFT
    EXIT BOTTOM LEFT BELOW BANK
    USE COINS ON MAN
    GOTO HOTEL
    ENTER HOTEL
    USE STEPS TO TOP FLOOR
    EXIT BOTTOM
    GO TO THE LAST DOOR ON THE RIGHT AND OPERATE IT
    ENTER ROOM
    ON BOAT : OPERATE BRACLET
    IN SEA : WHEN YOU ARE NEAR THE BOTTOM , OPERATE BRACLET , SWIM TO GIRL ,
    OPERATE GIRL. (QUICKLY)
    THIS NEXT BIT WILL ALSO TAKE A BIT OF PRACTICE SO KEEP ON TRYING AND
    SAVING QUITE REGULARY UNTIL YOU COMPLETE ALL THE MAZES
    OPERATE HALL DOOR
    ENTER ROOM
    OPERATE STATUES ARM
    USE LITTLE BOX ON SAFE DOOR
    OPERATE VALIDATION BUTTON
    USE UP & DOWN ARROWS TO CHANGE NUMBER
    (IF A LIGHT ON BOX GOES ON THIS MEANS THE NUMBER SHOWN GOES IN THAT 
    POSITION.E.G IF 5 IS SHOWN AND LIGHT 3 GOES ON THEN NUMBER 5 IS THE 
    NUMBER OF THE CODE.WHEN ALL NUMBERS ARE IN THE CORRECT POSITION,OPERATE
    LOCK COMBINATION.)
    WHEN ALL FOUR NUMBERS ARE IN THE RIGHT PLACE TURN LITTLE BOX OFF
    TAKE BOX
    OPERATE LOCK COMBINATION
    TAKE ENVELOPE
    OPERATE SEA WEED
    TAKE ELASTIC BAND
    CATCH MAN AVOIDING ROCKS
    AVOID MEN
    OPERATE PORTHOLE
    USE PEN ON LOCK (CAGE LOCK)
    USE WATCH ON LEFT WALL
    USE WATCH ON RIGHT WALL
    MOVE IN FRONT OF GRILL
    OPERATE GRILL
    FINISH MAZES (SAME METHODS AS BEFORE)
    MOVE ALONG WALL TO LEFT OF MIDDLE SHOWER
    OPERATE SOLDIER
    TAKE NAPKIN
    TAKE LACES
    TAKE BOOTS
    TAKE CLOTHES
    TAKE GLASS
    USE LACES ON SOLDIER
    USE NAPKIN ON SOLDIER
    EXIT BOTTOM
    EXIT BOTTOM
    ENTER TOP DOOR
    OPERATE BOTTOM RIGHT DRAWER
    EXAMINE DRAWER
    TAKE LACES
    USE LACES ON JOHN
    EXIT BOTTOM
    EXIT RIGHT
    ENTER DOOR
    EXAMINE CLOTHES
    TAKE MISSION INSTRUCTIONS
    USE GLASS ON FOUNTAIN
    OPERATE GARBAGE DUMP
    TAKE LIFEBOAT
    EXIT LEFT
    EXIT TOP
    EXIT TOP
    EXIT LEFT
    ENTER RIGHT DOOR
    USE GLASS ON OFFICER
    TAKE STAMP (WHILE OFFICER DRINKS)
    EXIT BOTTOM
    OPERATE CIGARETTE CASE
    OPERATE FIRST CIGARETTE
    USE CIGARETTE PAPER ON GLASS
    EXIT RIGHT
    EXIT BOTTOM
    ENTER DOOR
    TAKE INK PAD (RIGHT OF CHAIR)
    USE STAMP ON INK PAD
    USE STAMP ON MISSION INSTRUCTIONS
    EXIT LEFT
    EXIT TOP
    USE FINGER PRINT ON FINGER PRINT ID
    ENTER DOOR
    EXIT RIGHT
    USE MISSION ON MAIL BOX
    EXIT TOP
    USE ELECTRIC CABLE ON ELECTRIC SOCKET (NEXT TO TRASH CAN)
    OPERATE RAZOR
    USE RAZOR ON TRASH CAN
    EXIT RIGHT
    WAIT UNTIL A DISTRACTION IS CAUSED BY THE RAZOR AND THE USE THE BOTTOM
    CIGARETTE ON THE COMPUTER
    AFTER THE COMPUTER HAS BLOWN UP OPERATE OTTO
    (DO THIS NEXT BIT QUICKLY)
    AFTER FIGHT USE COMPACT DISC ON CD PLAYER
    EXIT THE DOOR ON THE LEFT
    USE ELASTIC BAND ON BOMB (WHEN ON HELECOPTER)
    OPERATE LIFE BOAT (WHEN FALLING)
